treach. The lobbying intensified during military tensions with India. Pakistan's army chief made claims about mediation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/debt-inflation-imf-dependence-pakistan-is-still-spending-900000-every-month-on-us-lobbying/articleshow/131456237.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/debt-inflation-imf-dependence-pakistan-is-still-spending-900000-every-month-on-us-lobbying/articleshow/131456237.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T12:51:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131456441,imgsize-55168.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[6 alligator-infested rivers in the US: From the St. Johns River in Florida to the Brazos River in Texas]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131457459.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/6-alligator-infested-rivers-in-the-us-from-the-st-johns-river-in-florida-to-the-brazos-river-in-texas/articleshow/131457459.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/6-alligator-infested-rivers-in-the-us-from-the-st-johns-river-in-florida-to-the-brazos-river-in-texas/articleshow/131457459.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T12:43:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131457814,imgsize-154696.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What looked like simple red stains turned out to be Britain’s oldest cave art from 17,100 years ago]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131457644.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-looked-like-simple-red-stains-turned-out-to-be-britains-oldest-cave-art-from-17100-years-ago/articleshow/131457644.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-looked-like-simple-red-stains-turned-out-to-be-britains-oldest-cave-art-from-17100-years-ago/articleshow/131457644.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T12:31:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131457727,imgsize-1810263.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Chinese philosopher Confucius: “Before you embark on a journey of revenge, dig two graves.”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131454380.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-chinese-philosopher-confucius-before-you-embark-on-a-journey-of-revenge-dig-two-graves-/articleshow/131454380.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-chinese-philosopher-confucius-before-you-embark-on-a-journey-of-revenge-dig-two-graves-/articleshow/131454380.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T09:44:50+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131454404,imgsize-61084.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[An alternative to the Strait of Hormuz? Why Iran is eyeing Yemen's Bab al-Mandab]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131453144.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Escalating Middle East tensions are now focusing on the Bab al-Mandab Strait, a crucial global shipping lane. Iran, via its Yemeni allies, may use this chokepoint to pressure adversaries, potentially disrupting vital oil and goods transit. This raises fears of wider conflict impacting international trade routes and energy markets.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/an-alternative-to-the-strait-of-hormuz-why-iran-is-eyeing-yemens-bab-al-mandab/articleshow/131453144.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/an-alternative-to-the-strait-of-hormuz-why-iran-is-eyeing-yemens-bab-al-mandab/articleshow/131453144.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T08:33:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131453526,imgsize-148350.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Operation Checkmate: 30 Indians held for illegally working as truck drivers in US, deportation likely]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131453412.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Border Patrol's Operation Checkmate has led to the arrest of approximately 30 Indian nationals working illegally as commercial truck drivers in Arizona. These individuals, along with others from different countries, are facing deportation. The operation aimed to enhance public safety by enforcing immigration laws and identifying undocumented drivers operating heavy vehicles.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/operation-checkmate-30-indians-held-for-illegally-working-as-truck-drivers-in-us-deportation-likely/articleshow/131453412.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/operation-checkmate-30-indians-held-for-illegally-working-as-truck-drivers-in-us-deportation-likely/articleshow/131453412.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T08:26:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131453460,imgsize-83136.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Bangladesh: Thousands gather to pay final respects to Awami League veteran, despite ban]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131452638.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Thousands gathered in Dhaka to honor Awami League veteran Tofail Ahmed, sparking speculation about the party's potential resurgence amidst a ban.  This event, coupled with claims of minimal reforms by the interim government and its alignment with certain parties, suggests a possible return for the Awami League. Meanwhile, a minority minister resigned citing health issues.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-thousands-gather-to-pay-final-respects-to-awami-league-veteran-despite-ban/articleshow/131452638.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-thousands-gather-to-pay-final-respects-to-awami-league-veteran-despite-ban/articleshow/131452638.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T06:45:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Ahsan Tasnim</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131452640,imgsize-34118.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why is HasanAbi barred from entering the UK? Twitch star claims visa was revoked ahead of major appearances]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131452401.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Twitch streamer HasanAbi has claimed that the United Kingdom revoked his visa, preventing him from attending several planned events and appearances in the country. Speaking during a livestream, he criticized the decision and linked it to broader political issues. The controversy quickly gained attention online, with supporters and critics debating his claims while questions remain about the circumstances behind the reported visa revocation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-is-hasanabi-barred-from-entering-the-uk-twitch-star-claims-visa-was-revoked-ahead-of-major-appearances/articleshow/131452401.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-is-hasanabi-barred-from-entering-the-uk-twitch-star-claims-visa-was-revoked-ahead-of-major-appearances/articleshow/131452401.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131452401,imgsize-39434.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why was Jack Doherty arrested? Viral handcuff video sparks heated debate across social media]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131452382.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A viral video showing streamer Jack Doherty in handcuffs and being escorted to a police car has sparked widespread debate online. While some viewers were shocked, many social media users questioned the footage's authenticity, calling it a staged stunt. The controversy comes weeks after Doherty claimed he had been placed under house arrest, adding more uncertainty to the situation and fueling speculation across the internet.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-was-jack-doherty-arrested-viral-handcuff-video-sparks-heated-debate-across-social-media/articleshow/131452382.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-was-jack-doherty-arrested-viral-handcuff-video-sparks-heated-debate-across-social-media/articleshow/131452382.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T05:32:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131452382,imgsize-61872.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hasan Piker says he was denied entry to the UK ahead of major speaking events]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131450098.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular online commentator Hasan Piker and media personality Cenk Uygur were barred from entering the United Kingdom. Their travel permissions were revoked just before scheduled speaking events. This unexpected development led to the cancellation of their appearances at SXSW London and the University of Oxford. The British Home Office stated their presence was not conducive to the public good.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hasan-piker-says-he-was-denied-entry-to-the-uk-ahead-of-major-speaking-events/articleshow/131450098.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/hasan-piker-says-he-was-denied-entry-to-the-uk-ahead-of-major-speaking-events/articleshow/131450098.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T02:19:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131450095,imgsize-697190.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US politician trolled for his 'HinJew' family photo: 'Your kids are 0% Jewish']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131450094.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-politician-trolled-for-his-hinjew-family-photo-your-kids-are-0-jewish/articleshow/131450094.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-politician-trolled-for-his-hinjew-family-photo-your-kids-are-0-jewish/articleshow/131450094.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T02:20:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131450104,imgsize-60546.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who was Dave Fiji? Indian-origin pilot killed in helicopter crash hours after marrying]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131449882.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-was-dave-fiji-indian-origin-pilot-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-georgia-hours-after-marrying-long-time-partner/articleshow/131449882.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-was-dave-fiji-indian-origin-pilot-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-georgia-hours-after-marrying-long-time-partner/articleshow/131449882.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-02T01:47:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131450040,imgsize-93322.cms"/></item></channel></rss>